items.title: What Stock Market Sell-Off? These 2 Dow Jones Dividend Stocks Are Near Their All-Time Highs
items.description: Stock market volatility is back, with the S&P 500, Nasdaq Composite, and Dow Jones Industrial Average all down year to date -- with their declines led by sell-offs in growth-focused sectors like technology and consumer discretionary.  Dow componentsÂ Procter & Gamble (NYSE: PG) and Coca-Cola (NYSE: KO) are hovering around their all-time highs.
